cs.CL, cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and specifically named entity recognition in Norwegian. It could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses a neural sequence labeling architecture for the analysis of the corpus. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of machine learning techniques for the annotation of the corpus. It could also be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of AI techniques for natural language processing. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as named entity recognition is an important task in information retrieval.
